    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/bb53c083a8fc996344f22432922b392a.poster.avif?t=1759617875\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/bb53c083a8fc996344f22432922b392a.webm?t=1759617875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/bb53c083a8fc996344f22432922b392a.mp4?t=1759617875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >汪汪救援队(<strong>Tenkemo</strong>)是一款温馨且充满乐趣与冒险的多人开放世界游戏！无论您是玩单人游戏还是与朋友们一起玩都能探索一个巨大的世界，收集资源、制作工具，建造从房屋到工厂的各类建筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索森林、洞穴与山脉，体验酷炫的天气变化与日夜交替。你的任务是什么？拯救并收集可爱的动物们，然后与它们组队，保护它们的王国免受企图占领的AI机器人的威胁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/cd3429dcbc9bee537dfc0cc102a274ae.poster.avif?t=1759617875\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/cd3429dcbc9bee537dfc0cc102a274ae.webm?t=1759617875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/cd3429dcbc9bee537dfc0cc102a274ae.mp4?t=1759617875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特色</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可单人或与朋友们一起玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满洞穴、森林与山脉的广大开放世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有天气系统与日夜交替</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源并开采材料</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作工具并建造房屋、工厂等更多建筑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集可爱动物并与它们并肩作战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义您的角色</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/8d90c1b8dc5151ec0df8c4949372a517.poster.avif?t=1759617875\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/8d90c1b8dc5151ec0df8c4949372a517.webm?t=1759617875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268370/extras/8d90c1b8dc5151ec0df8c4949372a517.mp4?t=1759617875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们仍在努力开发这款游戏，因此请加入我们的Discord社群，分享您的想法并帮助塑造爪印救援队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即加入愿望清单，并保持关注！</strong></p>",
